==Usage==
Simple usage example:

<pre>
{{en/Ambox| text = Some text.}}
</pre>
{{en/Ambox| text = Some text.}}
== List of parameters==
<pre>
{{en/Ambox| type       = delete / content / style / notice / move / protection
| image      = en/Picture.Png/Picture.png|alt=Picture
| text       = Text for a big box, for the top of articles.
| smallimage = Picture.Png OR Picture.Png|alt=Picture <-- not used yet
| smalltext  = Text for the top of article sections. <-- not used yet
}}
</pre>


=== Article message box types ===

The following examples use different '''type''' parameters but use no image parameters thus they use the default images for each type.

{{en/Ambox| type  = delete
| text  = type=<u>delete</u> – Deletion issues, such as {{en/S|en/Xxx}}.
}}
{{en/Ambox| type  = content
| text  = type=<u>content</u> – Content issues, such as {{en/S|en/Xxx}}.
}}
{{en/Ambox| type  = style
| text  = type=<u>style</u> – Style issues, such as {{en/S|en/Cleanup}}.
}}
{{en/Ambox| type  = notice
| text  = type=<u>notice</u> – Article notices, such as {{en/S|en/Current}}.
}}
{{en/Ambox| type  = move
| text  = type=<u>move</u> – Merge, split and transwiki proposals, such as {{en/S|en/Split}}.
}}
{{en/Ambox| type  = protection
| text  = type=<u>protection</u> – Protection notices, such as {{en/S|en/Xxx}}.
}}

=== Other images ===

The default images shown above are mostly for convenience. In many cases it is more appropriate to use more specific images. These examples use the '''image''' parameter to specify an image other than the default images.

{{en/Ambox| type  = notice
| image =en/Manual/OpenttdManual.png|alt= Openttd Manual
| text  = something something something something something.
}}

